spell.spellbladenext.vaulting_slam_minor: Use your weapon to vault into the air, slamming at the end of the cast for {damage} physical damage in an area. You are invulnerable while vaulting.
spell.oathswornpaladins.resonating_shiel: Slam your shield with your weapon, dealing {damage} armor based damage in an area. You count as blocking while channeling this ability.
